  "about_item": [
    "Enhanced Safety Dog Crate: Our dog crate furniture features dual security locks on both the front and side doors, ensuring safety for large dogs. Made with 1mm thick steel tubes, the dog crate offers high chew resistance. This design keeps high anxiety dogs secure when you're away, preventing escapes.",
    "Versatile Double-Door Design: The side door of the furniture dog crate allows for easy cleaning without blind spots. The sliding front door provides a smooth experience. If you want keep your dog crate open, it doesn't occupy extra space, allowing your dog to move freely.",
    "Easy Assembly: Includes all tools, a detailed guide, and videos for easy assembly. While the furniture dog crate can be assembled by one person, having help makes it quicker. Our 24/7 customer service is ready to assist with any installation issues.",
    "Durable and Functional: Crafted from thickened metal and wood, the furniture dog crate supports over 200lbs, making it ideal for medium dogs. The waterproof and scratch-resistant wooden boards are easy to clean, maintaining the decorative dog crate a fresh look.",
    "360° Feeding Rack: Equipped with a 360° rotatable elevated feeder and two 304 stainless steel bowls, the furniture dog crate makes feeding easy and simple..The feeder has 4 adjustable heights for comfort, and the rotatable design enhances feeding efficiency."
  ],
